			<action-date date="20130618">June 18, 2013</action-date>
			<action-desc>
        <sponsor name-id="G000567">Mr. Griffin of
			 Arkansas</sponsor> (for himself, <cosponsor name-id="J000174">Mr. Sam Johnson
			 of Texas</cosponsor>, and <cosponsor name-id="R000578">Mr.
			 Reichert</cosponsor>) introduced the following bill; which was referred to the
